AI and the World
----------------

There were two momentous AI announcements last week. First, from Technomanc=
ers ( https://technomancers.ai/japan-goes-all-in-copyright-doesnt-apply-to-=
ai-training/ ) :

In a surprising move, Japan=E2=80=99s government recently reaffirmed that i=
t will not enforce copyrights on data used in AI training. The policy allow=
s AI to use any data =E2=80=9Cregardless of whether it is for non-profit or=
 commercial purposes, whether it is an act other than reproduction, or whet=
her it is content obtained from illegal sites or otherwise.=E2=80=9D Keiko =
Nagaoka, Japanese Minister of Education, Culture, Sports, Science, and Tech=
nology, confirmed ( https://go2senkyo.com/seijika/122181/posts/685617 ) the=
 bold stance to local meeting, saying that Japan=E2=80=99s laws won=E2=80=
=99t protect copyrighted materials used in AI datasets.

I haven=E2=80=99t seen this news widely reported, and the linked article, w=
hich is in Japanese, doesn=E2=80=99t appear to be as definitive as presente=
d in this Technomancers article. In this case, though, I think it is useful=
 to assume it is true, and consider the implications: should Japan =E2=80=
=94 or any other country =E2=80=94 unequivocally state that AI training doe=
s not violate copyright ( which I think is correct ( https://stratechery.co=
m/2023/fair-use-and-model-training-getty-images-vs-stable-diffusion-adobes-=
regulatory-capture-bet/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0=
ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJzdHJhdGVjaGVyeS=
5wYXNzcG9ydC5vbmxpbmUiLCJlbnQiOnsidXJpIjpbImh0dHBzOi8vc3RyYXRlY2hlcnkuY29tL=
zIwMjMvZmFpci11c2UtYW5kLW1vZGVsLXRyYWluaW5nLWdldHR5LWltYWdlcy12cy1zdGFibGUt=
ZGlmZnVzaW9uLWFkb2Jlcy1yZWd1bGF0b3J5LWNhcHR1cmUtYmV0LyJdfSwiZXhwIjoxNjg4NTQ=
4Mjg3LCJpYXQiOjE2ODU5NTYyODcsImlzcyI6Imh0dHBzOi8vc3RyYXRlY2hlcnkucGFzc3Bvcn=
Qub25saW5lL29hdXRoIiwic2NvcGUiOiJmZWVkOnJlYWQgYXJ0aWNsZTpyZWFkIGFzc2V0OnJlY=
WQgY2F0ZWdvcnk6cmVhZCIsInN1YiI6IlJzZXVZRThqZ0hlUHBXSmYxZkFiNEMiLCJ1c2UiOiJh=
Y2Nlc3MifQ.hNfQ01U1IriIE15xWOgP72LpVmSGNZ7yIIGSnsEoJIxJ5p_AWNqbmq_AMOwsOW-v=
